          The Shadow of the Third Moon - Demo version


This is first Demo-Version of a new fanatastic ActionFlightSimulator.
TSOT3rdM uses a brandnew voxelengine technics, which brings a never
seen before realism flight simulation to your AMIGA. Forget ugly
vector-base flightsimulations.
The Game will be available on August 1997, direct from our local
Amiga-Dealer or from:

